<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉zmẗ whtʿdy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- ạ̉zmẗ whtʿdy ạ̹lh ạltʿwyḍạt ạ̹lhy ḥy
 ạ̉zmẗ whtʿdy ạ̹lh ạlbrkạt bạlkẖyr jạy
 1- hyʿwḍ snyn fạtt whyʿwḍ snyn rạḥt
 dạ ạ̹lhy ḥy ạ̹lhy ḥy
 2- tẖqty ạ̉nạ msẖ hṭrḥhạ tẖqty ạ̉nạ msẖ hạnzʿhạ
 dạ ạ̹lhy ḥy ạ̹lhy ḥy
 3- ạ̹lhy jạy bạlʿwyḍạt ạ̹lhy jạy bạlbrkạt
 dạ ạ̹lhy ḥy ạ̹lhy ḥy</lyrics>
<author>mylạd ʿdly, rwmạny slymạn</author>
<hymn_number>9597</hymn_number>
</song>